title: Gaia
typeOfFood: Vegan, Pizza, Chinese, Indian, International, Italian, Fast food, Juice bar, Bakery, European, Hungarian
description: An all-vegan restaurant opened Spring 2016. On the menu are cakes, pancakes, cupcakes, other desserts, fresh juice with no additives, pizza, salads, burritos and more. One of the chefs is vegan and Italian.
